What is Mockito? Spy vs Mock?
- Mockito = library for creating fake objects in tests.
- Mockito.mock(List.class); fake object base on class that do nothing on calling any its methods, unless we wrote when(mockList.size()).thenReturn(100);
- Mockito.spy(new ArrayList<>()); real object, even if we have when(spyList.size()).thenReturn(100); if first execute real logic, then override it with fake


